After denying a woman the extension she needs to 
keep her home, loan officer Christine Brown (Alison 
Lohman) sees her once-promising life take a startling 
turn for the worse. Christine is convinced she's 
been cursed by a Gypsy, but her boyfriend (Justin 
Long) is skeptical. Now, her only hope seems to 
lie in a psychic (Dileep Rao) who claims he can help 
her lift the curse and keep her soul from being 
dragged straight to hell.

Starring: Alison Lohman, Justin Long

Director: Sam Raimi
